  <p>
    Mobile applications handle sensitive user data, financial transactions, and personal communications, making them prime targets for attackers. <strong>Mobile Security Framework (MobSF)</strong> is an automated, all-in-one mobile application security testing framework that can perform static and dynamic analysis on Android, iOS, and Windows mobile apps. In this comprehensive guide, we'll focus on using MobSF for Android application security analysis.
  </p>

